data.description: Exquisite two-story McNair home within the exclusive guarded community of The Dominion. This beautiful home gives you plenty of space for entertaining with an interior that is bright and inviting with plenty of natural light beaming through the large windows showcasing 20 foot ceilings and an open floor plan.  This home features beautiful lighting fixtures, kitchen with custom cabinets, stainless steel appliances and sleek countertops with a large breakfast area. Luxurious master suite with a spa-like bath and spacious his and her closets. Ample storage, office and secondary bedroom down stairs make this a rare find. Upstairs you will find a gameroom and media room accompanied by a wet bar, a great place for family and friends to hang. There is an additional four spacious bedrooms each with their en-suite bathrooms.  This home has a oversized additional bonus room great for storage. Lavish greenery surround the outdoors complete with a summer kitchen and spacious yard. This property must be experienced in person to be able to take in all it has to offer.
